Install node.js
In node.js command prompt --> npm install -g @angular/cli
navigate to a new folder where u want to create a project.
create a new project with --> ng new projectname

Install Visual studio and open this project in VS.
This project will have a dumpy app. 
You can run it by command--> ng serve

http://localhost:4200 --> you can view app in the browser.

Yous can change codes in VS and work on.